article.headline: DeVries scores 29, leads Drake to 74-66 victory over Bradley

images.name: Bradley Braves vs. Drake Bulldogs: Game Highlights
images.caption: Bradley Braves vs. Drake Bulldogs: Game Highlights

article.linkText: DeVries scores 29, leads Drake to 74-66 victory over Bradley
article.story: DES MOINES, Iowa -- — Tucker DeVries scored 29 points and Drake beat Bradley 74-66 on Sunday night. DeVries added six rebounds and four steals for the Bulldogs (25-6, 16-4 Missouri Valley Conference). Kevin Overton made two 3-pointres and scored 13. Colby Garland had 10 points. Malevy Leons led the Braves (21-10, 13-7) with 18 points, six rebounds and four blocks. Duke Deen added 13 points and Darius Hannah scored 10. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
